    "headlineLine1": "Not an event.",
    "headlineLine2": "36 hours of building.",
    "paragraph1": "The Next Craft is the in-person hackathon by Crafter Station × Next. 36 hours of real work, running simultaneously in Lima, Bogotá and Guatemala, with 150 hackers solving real problems.",
